title: Inception
overview: A thief who steals corporate secrets through dream-sharing technology is given the inverse task of planting an idea.

title: The Godfather
overview: The aging patriarch of an organized crime dynasty transfers control to his reluctant son.

title: Interstellar
overview: A team of explorers travel through a wormhole in space in an attempt to ensure humanity's survival.

title: Parasite
overview: Greed and class discrimination threaten the newly formed symbiotic relationship between the wealthy Park family and the destitute Kim clan.

title: Spirited Away
overview: During her family's move to the suburbs, a sullen 10-year-old girl wanders into a world ruled by gods, spirits, and witches.

title: The Dark Knight
overview: Batman sets out to dismantle the remaining criminal organizations that plague Gotham.

title: Titanic
overview: A seventeen-year-old aristocrat falls in love with a kind but poor artist aboard the luxurious, ill-fated R.M.S. Titanic.

title: Avengers: Endgame
overview: After the devastating events of Avengers: Infinity War, the universe is in ruins.

title: The Matrix
overview: A computer hacker learns about the true nature of his reality and his role in the war against its controllers.

title: Coco
overview: Aspiring musician Miguel, confronted with his family's ancestral ban on music, enters the Land of the Dead.
